sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    actor User
    participant OTP as OTP Wrapper
    participant Redis as Redis Counters
    participant SMU as SMU Notification API

    loop each verify attempt
        User->>OTP: POST /otp/verify
        OTP->>Redis: check lock key and attempt count
        alt account already locked
            Redis-->>OTP: lock TTL remaining
            OTP-->>User: 429 rate limit exceeded
        else allowed to try
            OTP->>SMU: VerifyOTP
            alt wrong OTP
                SMU-->>OTP: invalid code
                OTP->>Redis: increment otp:rate key
                alt reached max attempts
                    OTP->>Redis: set otp:lock key with TTL
                    OTP-->>User: 429 account locked
                else still below limit
                    OTP-->>User: 200 verified=false
                end
            else correct OTP
                SMU-->>OTP: verified
                OTP->>Redis: clear attempt and lock keys
                OTP-->>User: 200 verified=true
            end
        end
    end
